{
  "texts": [
    "Deep learning, although offering high accuracy, often operates with an opaque decision-making strategy.",
    "To bolster decision-making integrity, trust, belief, fairness, reliability, and impartiality become paramount.",
    "It is essential to move beyond mere accuracy and address the interpretability of the models.",
    "Developing models that not only deliver accurate results but also offer clear explanations for their decisions is crucial for enhancing transparency and accountability in sentiment analysis.",
    "This approach ensures that the decision-making process is not only accurate but also comprehensible, fostering trust and confidence in the results generated by sentiment analysis models."
  ]
}